org.boon.json

Class JSONParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.boon.json.JSONParser

  • public class JSONParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Converts an input JSON String into Java objects works with Reader or String as input. Produces an Object which can be any of the basic JSON types mapped to Java.
